  "_comment": "Source -> doc map used by scripts/docs/check-doc-sync.mjs (Stop hook). Three target types per entry: `doc` (feature doc — required, exit-2 nag if missing), `onboardingFlows` (optional list of tour-flow IDs from the onboardingFlows registry below — exit-2 nag if any listed AND no `src/features/onboarding/**` file touched), `marketingModule` (optional desktop-modules.ts module ID — informational breadcrumb only, never exits 2 on its own). Skip patterns (tests, generated bindings, i18n, docs themselves) are handled inside the script.",
